I fixed it, never mind.
If you have the same error, I fixed it by going to Control pannel - System - Advanced - performance settings - Data execution prevention - Go to Add, and Add iw4mp.dat to that list. 

Only follow that if you have 
(0xc0000018) App error, or
(0xc0000005) App error

Hope this helps someone in the future.
